title: Ep. 593 - The Biden-Harris Ticket Goes Full Marxist
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, the Biden team is making its closing pitch to voters, and the closing pitch is full blown Marxism. Will it work or backfire? And if it does work, what does that say about our country? Also Five Headlines including cities bracing for leftist rioting after the election. If I was a leftist, I’d be pretty ashamed. Though if I was a leftist, I’d also be incapable of shame. And a special Double Cancellation today.
